The evidence with the title 'Health care advocacy group blasts insurers for ceo pay packages ... ' says Sep 16, 2009  ... The ad from Health Care For America Now says insurance CEOs make $ 24 million a year and that insurers deny 1 in 5 treatments prescribed by doctors .  ... We checked Forbes , which compiles the total compensation from public filings of salaries and stock options , and the $ 24 million figure does indeed jibe  ... 
